NOTES:

1/14/03: this is a clean distribution.  To build:
	bootstrap
	./configure
	make

	to remove the configure script and associated files type:
	bootstrap --clean

	to return the distribution to a clean state type:
	make distclean

	to remove intermediate files type:
	make clean
	
	make installs the libs in the $(PREFIX)/lib directory and the 
		necessary includes in $(PREFIX)/include
